==================== Input ====================
// Comments between a tagged template's tag and its quasi always attach to the
// quasi as leading comments, regardless of the surrounding whitespace (prettier#19345).
foo`` // comment 1
;
foo // comment 2
``;
foo // comment 3
`x`;
foo /* comment 4 */`
`;
foo /* comment 5 */
`
`;
foo /* comment 6 */
`x`;
foo // comment 7
`x`;
foo
/* comment 8 */
`x`;
foo
// comment 9
`x`;
bar(foo // comment 10
`x`);
bar(foo /* comment 11 */
`x`);

